name: Fat Trel
description: '''Martrel Reeves''' (born June 26, 1990), better known by his stage name '''Fat Trel''', is an American rapper. He was previously signed to [[Asylum Records]], [[Rick Ross]]'s record label [[Maybach Music Group]], an imprint of [[Atlantic Records]], and fellow DMV rapper [[Wale (rapper)|Wale]]'s label The Board Administration. From 2009 to 2016, Reeves released at least one solo mixtape per year.
